06ff"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Qu'est-ce que c'est que cette chose appelée Polars ?</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Caractéristiques principales</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Concepts clés</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Avantages</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Pourquoi devrais-tu utiliser Polars ?</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Performance</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Utilisabilité</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Popularité</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Durabilité</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Polars comparé à d'autres logiciels de traitement de données</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Pourquoi nous nous concentrons sur les Pythons</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Comment ce livre est organisé</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Une vitrine ETL</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Extrait</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Bonus : Visualisation des quartiers et des stations</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Transformer</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Bonus : Visualisation des déplacements quotidiens par arrondissement</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Charge</span><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao">Bonus : Devenir plus rapide en étant paresseux</span><span cla