lars-section-content-27" role="region" class="MuiAccordion-region css-1xdhyk6"><div class="MuiAccordionDetails-root css-106ff"></div></div></div></div></div></div></li></ul><button class="css-1a508d5">Show More</button></div></aside><div data-testid="main-content" class="css-1jl3w6t"><div data-testid="title-content"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h3 css-n450cf">Overview</h3><div data-testid="titleDescription" lang="fr" class="css-oeahc0"><span><span><div data-type="note"><p>Cet ouvrage a été traduit à l'aide de l'IA. Tes réactions et tes commentaires sont les bienvenus : <a href="mailto:translation-feedback@oreilly.com" onmousedown="dataLayer.push({&#39;event&#39;: &#39;eventTracker&#39;, &#39;eventCat&#39;: &#39;Email Clicks&#39;, &#39;eventAct&#39;:&#39;Click&#39;, &#39;eventLbl&#39;: &#39;translation-feedback@oreilly.com&#39;, &#39;eventVal&#39;: 0, &#39;nonInteraction&#39;: 0});">translation-feedback@oreilly.com</a></p></div><div><p>Libérez la puissance de Polars, un package Python pour transformer, analyser et visualiser des données. Dans ce guide pratique, Jeroen Janssens et Thijs Nieuwdorp vous présentent toutes les fonctionnalités de Polars et vous montrent comment l'utiliser pour des tâches concrètes telles que le data wrangling, l'analyse exploratoire des données, la construction de pipelines, etc.</p><p>Que tu sois un professionnel des données chevronné ou novice en science des données, tu maîtriseras rapidement l'API expressive de Polars et ses concepts sous-jacents. Tu n'as pas besoin d'avoir de l'expérience avec pandas, mais si c'est le cas, ce livre t'aidera à faire une transition en douceur. Les nombreux exemples pratiques et ensembles de données réels sont disponibles sur GitHub, ce qui te permet de suivre facilement.</p><ul><li>Traite les données provenant de CSV, Parquet, de feuilles de calcul, de bases de données et du Cloud</li><li>Acquiers une solide compréhension des expressions, les éléments constitutifs de chaque requête.</li><li>Gère des types de données complexes, y compris du texte, des données temporelles et des structures imbriquées.</li><li>Utilise les API « eager » et « lazy », et sache quand utiliser chacune d'elles</li><li>Visualise tes données avec Altair, hvPlot, plotnine et Great Tables</li><li>Étend Polars avec tes propres fonctions Python et plugins Rust</li><li>Tire parti de l'accélération GPU pour améliorer encore les performances</li></ul></div></span></span></div><div data-testid="start-trial" data-contextid="title-cta" class="css-bdp473"><h5 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h5 css-1g9gidf">Become an O’Reilly member and get unlimited access to this title plus top books and audiobooks from O’Reilly and nearly 200 top publishers, thousands of courses curated by job role, 150+ live events each month,<br>and much more.</h5><a class="MuiButtonBase-root MuiButton-root MuiButton-contained MuiButton-containedPrimary MuiButton-sizeMedium MuiButton-containedSizeMedium MuiButton-colorPrimary css-1ohi33g" tabindex="0" href="https://www.oreilly.com/start-trial/?next=/library/view/python-polars/9798341631595/" data-contextid="title-cta"><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 css-sbqy4j">Read now</p><p class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 css-2il9qw">Unlock full access</p></a></div><div class="css-rq7r3w"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h3 css-rosn43">More than 5,000 organizations count on O’Reilly</h3><div class="css-bn55w8"><img src="./Python Polars _ le guide définitif [Book]_files/AirBnb-DGMKJRKH.svg" alt="AirBnb" class="css-19svn3s"><img src="./Python Polars _ le guide définitif [Book]_files/BlueOrigin-4RWFILGY.svg" alt="BlueOrigin" class="css-19svn3s"><img src="./Python Polars _ le guide définitif [Book]_files/EA-7HTQJYZU.svg" alt="Electronic Arts" class="css-19svn3s"><img src="./Python Polars _ le guide définitif [Book]_files/HomeDepot-WLPY677N.svg" alt="HomeDepot" class="css-lzuxrz"><img src="./Python Polars _ le guide définitif [Book]_files/Nasdaq-4FUP2MSJ.svg" alt="Nasdaq" class="css-19svn3s"><img src="./Python Polars _ le guide définitif [Book]_files/Rakuten-BLMSPBIO.svg" alt="Rakuten" class="css-19svn3s"><img src="./Python Polars _ le guide définitif [Book]_files/TCS-NRQ65RC6.svg" alt="Tata Consultancy Services" class="css-19svn3s"></div><hr class="css-educav"><div data-testid="quotations" class="css-1whw8ho"><div class="css-1km0bek"><img src="./Python Polars _ le guide définitif [Book]_files/QuotationMark-QYP5HNGW.svg" width="28" height="20" alt="QuotationMark"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-textBody css-1k5fhp8">O’Reilly covers everything we've got, with content to help us build a world-class technology community, upgrade the capabilities and competencies of our teams, and improve overall team performance as well as their engagement.</span><h5 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h5 css-9835eh">Julian F.</h5><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-cardFooter css-1s0xpk1">Head of Cybersecurity</span></div><div class="css-1km0bek"><img src="./Python Polars _ le guide définitif [Book]_files/QuotationMark-QYP5HNGW.svg" width="28" height="20" alt="QuotationMark"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-textBody css-1k5fhp8">I wanted to learn C and C++, but it didn't click for me until I picked up an O'Reilly book. When I went on the O’Reilly platform, I was astonished to find all the books there, plus live events and sandboxes so you could play around with the technology.</span><h5 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h5 css-9835eh">Addison B.</h5><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-cardFooter css-1s0xpk1">Field Engineer</span></div><div class="css-1km0bek"><img src="./Python Polars _ le guide définitif [Book]_files/QuotationMark-QYP5HNGW.svg" width="28" height="20" alt="QuotationMark"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-textBody css-1k5fhp8">I’ve been on the O’Reilly platform for more than eight years. I use a couple of learning platforms, but I'm on O'Reilly more than anybody else. When you're there, you start learning. I'm never disappointed.</span><h5 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h5 css-9835eh">Amir M.</h5><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-cardFooter css-1s0xpk1">Data Platform Tech Lead</span></div><div class="css-1km0bek"><img src="./Python Polars _ le guide définitif [Book]_files/QuotationMark-QYP5HNGW.svg" width="28" height="20" alt="QuotationMark"><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-textBody css-1k5fhp8">I'm always learning. So when I got on to O'Reilly, I was like a kid in a candy store. There are playlists. There are answers. There's on-demand training. It's worth its weight in gold, in terms of what it allows me to do.</span><h5 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h5 css-9835eh">Mark W.</h5><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-cardFooter css-1s0xpk1">Embedded Software Engineer</span></div></div></div><div data-testid="recommendations" class="css-1tqpheq"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h3 css-1qrsk19">You might also like</h3><div class="css-6yczmy"><div data-testid="recommendation-item" class="css-1cqyldw"><div class="css-1p94oar"><a class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-inherit MuiLink-root MuiLink-underlineNone css-fbgf3n" href="https://www.oreilly.com/library/view/-/9798341619975/"><img src="./Python Polars _ le guide définitif [Book]_files/saved_resource(1)" alt="Spark : Le guide définitif" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="css-nmqdl1"></a></div><div><a class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-text MuiLink-root MuiLink-underlineNone css-14sagay" href="https://www.oreilly.com/library/view/-/9798341619975/"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h3 css-10ohu4w" data-testid="recommendation-title">Spark : Le guide définitif</h3></a><span class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-uiBodySmall css-1k3yao" data-testid="recommendation-author">Bill Chambers, Matei Zaharia</span></div></div><div data-testid="recommendation-item" class="css-1